"{\"uid\": \"the42.ie-rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024\", \"text\": \"RACHEL DARRAGH IS out of the Olympics following a straight sets defeat to Spaniard\\u00a0Carolina Marin.  The Donegal woman lost out 21-5, 21-5 to an opponent who is a former Olympic champion and three-time world champion.  Advertisement  \\ud83c\\udff8 | BADMINTONRachael Darragh's maiden Olympic Games has concluded with a straight sets defeat to 2016 gold medallist Carolina Marin at La Chapelle Arena.#TeamIreland|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/gwFVkpja11- Team Ireland (@TeamIreland)July 31, 2024  \\ud83c\\udff8 | BADMINTONRachael Darragh's maiden Olympic Games has concluded with a straight sets defeat to 2016 gold medallist Carolina Marin at La Chapelle Arena.#TeamIreland|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/gwFVkpja11  Marin, the fourth seed, was favoured strongly to win this group match. Darragh competed gamely but the difference in class to one of the truly elite competitors in the sport was evident.  If the 26-year-old from\\u00a0Raphoe leaves Paris with regrets, it will be in not getting over the line against\\u00a0Switzerland's Jenjira Stadelmann yesterday, despite being in control for much of the contest and seeing a match point slip away.  Darragh had match point at 22-21 over the Swiss woman in the second set only for Stadelmann to survive it and win the set 24-22, levelling the match before clinching it with a 21-15 win in the third.    The group of three which included Stadelmann, a European bronze medallist, and Marin was a tough draw for Darragh, whose singles campaign is now over.  To embed this post, copy the code below on your site  600px wide<iframe width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0px;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.the42.ie/https://www.the42.ie/rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024/?embedpost=6451374&width=600&height=460\\\" ></iframe>  400px wide<iframe width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0px;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.the42.ie/https://www.the42.ie/rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024/?embedpost=6451374&width=400&height=460\\\" ></iframe>  300px wide<iframe width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0px;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.the42.ie/https://www.the42.ie/rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024/?embedpost=6451374&width=300&height=460\\\" ></iframe>  Access to the comments facility has been disabled for this user  Create an email alert based on the current article\"}"